Others: The International Cricket Council has announced the schedule of ICC T20 World Cup 2021, and Oman Cricket Academy Ground, Al Amerat is one of the venues selected to host the tournament.
A total of 6 matches will be played at the Oman Cricket Academy Ground, Al Amerat, with the first match being Oman Vs Papua New Guinea on October 17.
The price for the Oman Stadium Ticket is 26.41 USD.
Hotels near Oman Cricket Academy Ground, Al Amerat include Ibis Hotel Muscat, Al Amerat Hotel, Al Maha International Hotel, and Centara Muscat Hotel Oman.
